    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just a break or a dry spell. it feels more permanent than that. like the actual core of who i am—the part that made life worth anything—is just dead. if there's no art, no creation, no way to connect to the world... then what's the point of the rest of this? it just feels like i'm performing the act of being alive for no reason.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
