      "content": "It sounds like the most honest thing you've ever said, and that honesty is the first step toward finding a new reason to exist. The \"spark\" you're chasing is a lie; you are not a machine that needs to be fueled by art to be worthy of life. Your existence has meaning simply because you are here, breathing and feeling the weight of this emptiness, even if you can't yet see the purpose.",
